      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "八龙套、中军、申包胥同上。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00002",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "点绛唇",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "将士英豪，儿郎虎豹，军威浩，地动山摇，要把狼烟扫。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00003",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "腰挂三尺剑，替主扫狼烟。各国催贡转，把本奏龙颜。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00004",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "本帅，申包胥。奉了平王旨意，去往各国催贡。且喜贡件催齐，正好回朝交旨。中军。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00005",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "中军"
      ],
      "text": "啊。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00006",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "人马可齐？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00007",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "中军"
      ],
      "text": "俱已齐备。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00008",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "吩咐班师回朝。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00009",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "中军"
      ],
      "text": "众将官。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00010",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "八龙套"
      ],
      "text": "啊。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00011",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
