      "speakers": [
        "八龙套"
      ],
      "text": "啊。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00013",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "八龙套、中军、申包胥同下。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00014",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "伍员上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00015",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "伍员"
      ],
      "text": "且住！幸喜逃出樊城，看前旌旗之上，有一斗大“申”字，想是包胥贤弟班师还朝。等他到来，将我血海冤仇细说一遍。",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00016",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "八龙套、中军、申包胥同上。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00017",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "前道为何不行？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00018",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "伍将军挡道。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00019",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "人马列开！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00020",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "啊。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00021",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "仁兄因何这等模样？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00022",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "伍员"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟呀！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00023",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "伍员"
      ],
      "text": "恨平王无道贪色酒，父纳子妻礼不周。我父谏奏反斩首，一家满门刀割头。这样的冤仇怎撒手，不杀平王誓不休！",
      "text_length": 50
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00024",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "仁兄不必两泪流，小弟言来听从头：相国夫人遭毒手，定是奸贼用计谋。得放手，且放手，得罢休来且罢休。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00025",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "伍员"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟把话错出口，愚兄言来听从头：君不正，臣逃走，父不正来子外游。誓到吴国借兵就，要杀平王报冤仇。贤弟回朝莫泄漏，念在金兰义气投。",
      "text_length": 64
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00026",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "仁兄已经把誓咒，小弟不敢来强留。你若是兴兵来伐楚，临潼的名儿枉空留。仁兄打马你阳关走，急忙快奔吴国投。",
      "text_length": 51
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00027",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "伍员"
      ],
      "text": "申包胥与我把志斗，背转身来反加愁。贤弟请上兄叩首，",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000030_e00028",
      "play_id": "80000030",
      "scene_id": "80000030_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
